{"tid":226501,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"各位請挽留粉俠傳作者袁生Orz...","createTime":"2017-05-02T14:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T05:51:32.000Z","uid":45713,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4898f7570d53c1e2fa61901d365f698c72d26d91","tid":226501,"uid":45713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/226229/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/226229/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n唔想佢走<br />\n每日我都會按佢profile page睇佢新post"},{"pid":"f7f550f6b649180241f88871034601e4861f38f6","tid":226501,"uid":22209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:21:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/226229/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/226229/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n唔想佢走<br />\n每日我都會按佢profile page睇佢新post</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n背句經典對白黎聽聽先喇"},{"pid":"bd9df4289db1c13aefeb02490d437a490a87ca9b","tid":226501,"uid":45713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:27:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/226229/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/226229/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n唔想佢走<br />\n每日我都會按佢profile page睇佢新post</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n背句經典對白黎聽聽先喇</blockquote><br />\n咁多想背邊句？"},{"pid":"b39b40d8cb4f0cb53720b1d8f68cd027eceb8906","tid":226501,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T14:43:04.000Z","msg":"挽你老母"},{"pid":"3925b3a27cb2ac80d9b4e839fc7db7f580828155","tid":226501,"uid":45713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>挽你老母</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a7b1ad42427aac9e441ef5f112f2c259b6f521","tid":226501,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T15:36:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2e1ea716ef5e613560d308ad0d81b3780ecc4ff2","tid":226501,"uid":45713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T15:53:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/133039_2e8b09b5baf684e56867e1bf4670e7ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F133039_2e8b09b5baf684e56867e1bf4670e7ff.jpg&h=17b70ce7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖為獲獎作品「粉俠傳」封面<br />\n<br />\n一名32歲、熱愛畫漫畫的青年，去年中抱著一試無妨的心態，報名參加日本「アホ漫畫大賞」，首次投稿海外的他「一擊即中」，奪得「トラップ作品特別賞」，是入圍及得獎者中唯一的香港人。擁有一手獨特畫風的他，慨嘆在香港畫漫畫並無出路，最大心願是能在台灣或日本發展漫畫事業，寄語其他熱愛畫漫畫的年輕人，「香港人忌才，經常恥笑我嘔心瀝血嘅作品，要發展就唔好喺香港」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/06/133340_11e7c370ff0b218a6c1cdcc2785a028d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F06%2F133340_11e7c370ff0b218a6c1cdcc2785a028d.jpg&h=e961fc77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作者其他系列作品「神龍刺青」<br />\n<br />\n32歲的袁偉德，筆名「袁崇煥」，曾以「無牌出版社有限公司」名義，於自設網站發佈多部獨立作品，惟作品並沒有得到香港人重視，多年來一直「貼錢都冇人要」，甚至經常被網民恥笑他的創意。他坦言自小喜歡畫畫，畫漫畫的年資已經有十多年，已經有日本專業畫師的水準。去年7月，他在書展中因好奇走到「馬鹿漫畫學校」的攤位，科主任馬華先生向他遞上「アホ漫畫大賞」的參賽表格，袁先生抱著一試無妨的心態，毅然填表參賽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2215W9o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2215W9o.jpg&h=7e03a83f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖為袁先生獲獎作品「粉伏傳」內頁<br />\n<br />\n15分鐘內趕工　友人協助翻譯　<br />\n<br />\n短短15分鐘內，他需要完成37頁的故事，還要拜託友人將中文對白翻譯成日文，「加上日本漫畫中有好多擬聲詞，係用嚟帶動故事，例如日本人食飯都會有『咕嚕咕嚕』嘅聲，畫嘅時候要一路參考日漫，呢個都係一個難處」。即便如此，他還是取得佳績，在云云參賽者中，奪得「トラップ作品特別賞」，是入圍及得獎者中唯一的香港人，一夜間聲名大噪，成為香港漫畫界的龍頭大哥。</blockquote><br />\n唔想佢走<br />\n係連登難得既一名高質會員"},{"pid":"a8ab501dc8f69cdb8d8ddf0bc4819d7c08647c8f","tid":226501,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T15:54:33.000Z","msg":"挽留"},{"pid":"88268a7da476d313f70eadaff19491ff594d3e01","tid":226501,"uid":106030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T15:57:05.000Z","msg":"輓聯"},{"pid":"c78883a32482f5b7119ec270c206bc631d